rows.label: qev011702_MSG0001
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0002
rows.name: Huh? Captain, is that you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0003
rows.name: Er, Chief! Sorry. I meant Chief.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0004
rows.name: What, uh... What brings you all the way out here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0005
rows.name: Me? Oh, I'm just, uh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0006
rows.name:
Just on patrol! All's well on the front lines, [ST:gender p1=sir p2=ma'am ]!
Nothing to report![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0007
rows.name: ...Huh? Captured? Me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0008
rows.name:
What are you talking about, Chief?
I'm right here, free as a bird![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0009
rows.name:
You sure you didn't stumble into some...
incredibly elaborate trap?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_JNK0010
rows.name: Suspect

rows.label: qev011702_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Mia why she is here exactly.

rows.label: qev011702_JNK0020
rows.name: Trust

rows.label: qev011702_SEL0021
rows.name: Thank Mia for the warning and ask about the trap.

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0010
rows.name:
What's that? Why am I here?
Like, in the philosophical sense?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0011
rows.name: That's a pretty deep question...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0012
rows.name:
I mean, really, why are any of us—
...Not what you meant. Right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0013
rows.name:
I came out here for the money, same as every
other BLADE! I mean, obviously.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0014
rows.name:
Nobody would risk their neck for idle curiosity,
least of all me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0015
rows.name:
And why slave for others? Money's the only
thing that'll never betray you. Heh.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0016
rows.name:
Anyway, I heard there was a lot of treasure here
in Cauldros, so I came to grab my share.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0017
rows.name:
At least, that was the plan.
Getting captured? Not so much.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0018
rows.name: But I've TOTALLY learned that lesson![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0021
rows.name:
Oh, you didn't know? There's tons of sinister traps
around these parts. Those xenoforms sure are tricky!
You gotta keep your head on a swivel![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0022
rows.name: Not like you need me to tell YOU that, Chief.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0023
rows.name:
I've got a long ways to go before I can teach you
anything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0024
rows.name:
And Instructor Walter, well... He's basically
given up on me at this point...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0025
rows.name:
Er, I mean...hey! Good riddance to that guy!
He's a total pain, in case you didn't know.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0026
rows.name: Not like you, er, Chief. You're amazing...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0027
rows.name:
He's all "blah blah responsibility," and he kinda smells
like a Prone's thong if you stand too close. But you...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0028
rows.name: You're perfect. We should totally—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0029
rows.name: Er, what's with the skeptical look there, Chief?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0030
rows.name:
Did I say something out of character?
...Uh, for me, I mean?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_JNK0030
rows.name: Accuse

rows.label: qev011702_SEL0031
rows.name: Draw your weapon as you accuse Mia of deception.

rows.label: qev011702_JNK0040
rows.name: Trust

rows.label: qev011702_SEL0041
rows.name: Give Mia the benefit of the doubt.

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0031
rows.name: Whoa whoa whoa WHOA![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0032
rows.name: What's with the weapons and the bloodlust, Chief?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0033
rows.name:
It's me! Cute little Mia! Why're you going
all crazy all of a sudden?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0034
rows.name: This is nuts! ...Also super annoying.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0035
rows.name: ...INSOLENT FOOL![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0037
rows.name:
Whew! Good ol' Chief, always believing
whatever you tell [ST:gender p1=him p2=her ].[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0038
rows.name:
It's almost too easy. Like, how stupid can you be?
Are you TRYING to get killed, you FOOL?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0039
rows.name:
...Whoops. That last line broke character, huh?
Er... Ha ha! Ha ha ha... Ha?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev011702_MSG0040
rows.name:
Damn you, human! This wouldn't have happened if
I'd had time to complete a full identity scan![ST:wait ]
